    Improved performance of compute values kernel by ~1.3x by using atomicCAS and atomicAdd.

    Removed old method of updating variables and then checking for overwrites.

    Updated all files to use new hash container functions.

    Now we're using atomics, we don't need insert_with_duplicates/clear_all.

    Added currently unused code for issuing rows by warp, may improve performance in the future if more cache bound.

